                        <title type="incomplete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3633Miracle">ተአምሪሃ፡ 
                           <sic resp="DR">ለእግዚእትነ</sic>፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ በ፪፡
                           ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ጸሎታ፡ ወበረከታ፡ ወምሕረተ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወልዳ፡ የሃሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ገብራ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8346sahlase">ሣህለ፡ ሥላሲ።</persName>
              ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</title>
                        <note>The explicit also mentions the name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8346sahlase">Śahla Śǝllāse</persName>.</note>
                        <note>The name of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8346sahlase">Śahla Śǝllāse</persName> has been substituted for the name of the previous owner, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10813WalattaH">Wälättä Ḥǝywät</persName>
